<emphasis id="B913C227A472FF95FB2FEEBBF69CF920" bold="true" box="[1166,1206,1688,1712]" pageId="22" pageNumber="61">F—</emphasis>
Subatrial/ atrial region composed exclusively of diactines (arrow). Abbreviations: at—Atrium and ct—cortex.
